title: QB & RB Rookie Preview + Fantasy Crushes - Fantasy Football Podcast for 4/5
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, it’s time to talk rookies! Andy, Mike, and Jason break down the top incoming rookies at quarterback and running back! Plus, a look at current players with the most to lose for fantasy football after the NFL Draft. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for April 5th, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(04:10) - Quick Question - Players to Lose Value
(12:15) - NFL News 
(19:30) - 2022 Rookies // NFL Draft
(20:05) - Rookie Quarterbacks
(20:10) - Malik Willis
(26:15) - Kenny Pickett
(30:10) - Matt Corral
(33:20) - Rookie Running Backs
(37:40) - Breece Hall
(42:25) - Kenneth Walker III
(45:45) - Isaiah Spiller
(50:40) - Rachaad White, Tyler Allgeier, James Cook, Tyler Badie
